<section class="bg-bg-secondary py-25">
  <div class="fade-on-scroll container mx-auto max-w-300 px-5">
    <div class="mb-15 text-center">
      <span
        class="text-accent mb-2.5 block text-[0.9rem] tracking-[3px] uppercase"
        >Tu Experiencia</span
      >
      <h2 class="text-[3rem]">EL RITUAL</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 text-center md:grid-cols-3">
      <div
        class="hover:border-accent group border border-[#222] p-7.5 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2.5 hover:bg-[#111]">
        <i
          class="ph ph-pencil-simple-slash text-accent mb-5 block text-[3rem] transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110"
        ></i>
        <h3 class="mb-3.75 text-[1.5rem]">1. Consulta</h3>
        <p class="text-[#888]">
          Analizamos tu idea, zona y referencias para crear un concepto único.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="hover:border-accent group border border-[#222] p-7.5 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2.5 hover:bg-[#111]">
        <i
          class="ph ph-paint-brush-broad text-accent mb-5 block text-[3rem] transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110"
        ></i>
        <h3 class="mb-3.75 text-[1.5rem]">2. Diseño</h3>
        <p class="text-[#888]">
          Preparamos el arte digital y ajustamos el "stencil" a tu anatomía.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="hover:border-accent group border border-[#222] p-7.5 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2.5 hover:bg-[#111]">
        <i
          class="ph ph-drop text-accent mb-5 block text-[3rem] transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110"
        ></i>
        <h3 class="mb-3.75 text-[1.5rem]">3. Sesión</h3>
        <p class="text-[#888]">
          Ejecución precisa en un ambiente estéril y privado.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
